summaries.short: Ray steps out of the coaching box; Tanya's deception is exposed; Jessica scratches an old itch.
summaries.full: With his team's future wracked by vandals, Ray agrees to participate in a student-alumni baseball game, but an unexpected warm-up with Claire threatens to put him on the disabled list. Fed up with Tanya's greed and confused by Mike's request for a donation, Frances doubts their affair. Jessica's old itch resurfaces, prompting Ronnie to deliver a sideline ultimatum to her ex.

summaries.short: Mike accuses Ray of betrayal; Ronnie vents his frustrations with Jessica at a dermatology banquet; Tanya lashes out at her co-workers.
summaries.full: A bad day at school gets worse when Mike accuses Ray of betrayal. Ronnie vents his frustrations with Jessica at a dermatology banquet, sending his wife running for the exits. Empowered by confession, Tanya lashes out at Ray, Lenore, and Horny Patty.

summaries.short: A new client forces Ray to choose cultural sides; Lenore seethes after learning of Tanya's duplicity.
summaries.full: A container of hummus puts Ray in the unenviable position of choosing cultural sides between Yael and a new client named Samara. Already upset after squandering her recent windfall, Tanya catches Ray in a cover-up--and turns to Charlie for some stress relief. Lenore seethes after learning of Tanya's duplicity; Liz surprises Ray with a revelation about her personal life.

summaries.short: (Season Two Finale) Ray eyes a possible second chance with Jessica; Tanya tries to make amends for her duplicity.
summaries.full: Season Two Finale. Eyeing a possible second chance with Jessica, Ray contemplates a break from the business--but Lenore may not be willing to give him up without a fight. An emotionally frayed Tanya visits Frances and Ray to try to make amends. After getting a lift from Mindy, Ronnie returns home to find that Jessica has made a decision that could impact both their futures.
